    "name": "潜行者2：切尔诺贝利之心",
    "steam_appid": 1643320,
    "required_age": "18",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入群组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入我们的中文讨论组！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《潜行者2：切尔诺贝利之心》官方QQ交流群：813270250</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索传奇的《潜行者》世界，同时体验：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>融合第一人称射击、恐怖元素和沉浸式模拟的独特游戏玩法 </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提供多条路径选项的非线性故事，最终导向不同游戏结局 </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使用尖端摄影测量和扫描技术开发的标杆级别画面 </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>先进的AI系统，即便是最硬核的游戏玩家也需要全力以赴 </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“A-life 2.0”生命模拟系统，为游戏世界注入全新活力 </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>饥饿、睡眠、流血、辐射等富有沉浸感的生存机制，让游戏玩法更加丰富多样 </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态的昼夜交替和天气变化，为游戏体验带来更多的真实感 </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>支持加入Mod，让创意十足的游戏玩家能够自由扩展和丰富游戏世界</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多人模式将在发布后作为免费更新添加</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/5ca350028fdf4a74977135c2a383df4a.poster.avif?t=1771271884\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/5ca350028fdf4a74977135c2a383df4a.webm?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/5ca350028fdf4a74977135c2a383df4a.mp4?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2006年第二次核反应堆爆炸事件发生后，切尔诺贝利封锁区早已面目全非。 封锁区内到处都是残暴的变种生物、致命的异常现象和交战不休的诸多派系，要想在此处生存可谓十分艰难。 然而，价值惊人的神器还是引来了众多“潜行者”，他们冒险闯入封锁区，想要从中大捞一笔，甚至还有人试图挖掘掩藏在切尔诺贝利核心地带的真相。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在栩栩如生的开放世界中谱写史诗级非线性故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演独自行动的潜行者，在64平方公里的辐射区内探索栩栩如生的拟真开放世界，地图中的各种环境将从不同的角度映衬出世界末日后的残破气息。 在情节分支高度自由的史诗篇章中选择你的发展路径，穿越辐射区，找到属于自己的归宿，同时决定人类社会的未来命运。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/4b696f7d7ad6255631565b673c184ca0.poster.avif?t=1771271884\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/4b696f7d7ad6255631565b673c184ca0.webm?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/4b696f7d7ad6255631565b673c184ca0.mp4?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >类型多样的敌人和上百种武器组合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接触不同派系的成员，决定谁值得信赖，谁应该挨枪子。 与类型多样的敌人展开激烈的枪战，敌人会采用不同的战术来试图取得胜利。 在30多种不同类型的武器中尽情挑选，你还可以自行更换武器配件，装配出数百种规格独特的致命枪械。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/8c017978a951f8ef2f4eb8a7ee6701a6.poster.avif?t=1771271884\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/8c017978a951f8ef2f4eb8a7ee6701a6.webm?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/8c017978a951f8ef2f4eb8a7ee6701a6.mp4?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >行为模式各异的传奇变种生物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好遭遇可怕的变种生物，这些生物会根据不同的行为模式与你展开搏杀。 每个变种生物都可能拥有不同子类型的行为模式，因而玩家更难对它们的攻击行为作出预测。 真正的极度危险隐藏在巢穴区域，在那里变种生物会成群结队地展开狩猎活动。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/1174f706e050e6acf2ec51f4cf74e276.poster.avif?t=1771271884\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/1174f706e050e6acf2ec51f4cf74e276.webm?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/1174f706e050e6acf2ec51f4cf74e276.mp4?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >价值惊人的神器和无情的异常事件</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >封锁区内最有价值的神器和秘密都藏匿在最危险的地方。 当你搜寻散落在封锁区内价值连城的神器时，别忘了提防危险的异常现象和极具毁灭性的大型罕见异常现象。 你有勇气前往尸横遍野的封锁区，揭开此处掩藏的惊天秘密吗？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/6cb3b40ecc755492abcdf40670132e30.poster.avif?t=1771271884\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/6cb3b40ecc755492abcdf40670132e30.webm?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/6cb3b40ecc755492abcdf40670132e30.mp4?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>潜行者们，猎杀行动开始！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/e74e4d157adcd486bd2bcb7a01947ccd.poster.avif?t=1771271884\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/e74e4d157adcd486bd2bcb7a01947ccd.webm?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1643320/extras/e74e4d157adcd486bd2bcb7a01947ccd.mp4?t=1771271884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
